name: Remembrace
description: Fashion is identified with the trend of women's clothing, which is the most hedonistic gender in consuming fashion, so that fashion waste is increasingly found.  Reduce from fashion waste is a process of remembering the story behind these fabrics that have a trend period to describe their identity.  Memorial, an effort to reflect on oneself during the pandemic, many things have changed instantly.  Where each fist is a sign of remembering an event, both good and bad.
